title: Is the UI ready for community beta?
body:
Shall we invite community members to a closed beta test of the DAO UI?Testing scope will include the landing page (News), Voting, Airdrop, and a minimalist Marketplace with one Vault.

Will take place on the Rinkeby testnet.
author: 0xf994f79590e9b9418F0dE031055d9E42B585ec5d
